<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634127389520593044" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634134213002274029">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The demonstrated <em>ListBox </em>contains defined <em>DataSource </em>as table 'Customer' of DataBase. The table contains 'CustomerID', 'ContactName' and other columns. The 'CustomerID' column is set as value of the <em>ListBox</em> <em>ValueMember </em>property and the 'ContactName' column is set as value of the <em>ListBox DisplayMember </em>property.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>ListBox </em>contains the following properties for binding data:<br /><em>DataSource </em>&ndash; defines the data source that the connector binds to;<br /><em>ColorMember </em>&ndash; defines the color member of the data sources;<br /><em>DisplayMember </em>- specifies the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by <em>DataSource </em>property. The property is displayed as text of the item. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;);<br /><em>ValueMember </em>&ndash; defines value of the <em>ListBox </em>item. Represents the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by the <em>DataSource </em>property. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;);<br /><em>ImageMember </em>- defines image for the <em>ListBox </em>item. Represents the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by the <em>DataSource </em>property. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;).<br /> And the following events:<br /><em>DataSourceChanged </em>&ndash; occurs when value of the <em>DataSource </em>property is changed. <br /><em>DisplayMemberChanged </em>&ndash; occurs when value of the <em>DisplayMember </em>property is changed.<br /><em>ValueMemberChanged </em>- occurs when value of the <em>ValueMember </em>property is changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
